com.appboy.events

Class InAppMessageEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.appboy.events.InAppMessageEvent

  • public final class InAppMessageEvent
extends java.lang.Object
    When Appboy receives a new in-app message in a server response, this event is fired. The message itself is provided along with the id of the user that the message is for (or null if no user id was set).
